description:
This Womens Ministries worldwide virtual conference is for all women looking for hope and comfort in this time of COVID-19. The event is filled with music and video reports from women around the world showing what they have done to help others during COVID. You will hear seminars that will uplift, encourage and inform you. Enjoy and be blessed.
